      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Desert Lost and Found",
        "Client": "Devoted Brother",
        "Description": "My li\u0027l bro suddenly spouted\r\noff about heading to the Sandy\r\nPlains. When I dragged the\r\nreason out of him, he said his\r\nbuddy lost his \u0022treasure\u0022 there.\r\nWhat\u0027s a bro to do? I\u0027ll comb\r\nthe sand, you watch my back.",
